    added ImplKeyboard and ImplMouse, their implementation and adapted Mouse and Keyboard classes
    added logical to physical button map to keyboard and mouse
    removed get/set title and icon from decorations
    added support for shift and caps lock to character sanitizer
    moved all kayboard related code from swing impl window to swing impl keyboard
    added numlock, capslock and scrolllock to keyboard classes
    moved get/set Cursor from window to Mouse, then using synchronization instead
    removed get/set Icon from window, using synchronization instead
    removed get/set title from window, using synchronization instead
